description: I just finished editing my video from the party last week and to see the stuff again made me so horny that I had to go out hunting again. It was a bit later already and I went straight to the nearest metro station to find today´s Mr.Right. It didn´t take long until I noticed a young guy rushing out of the station. He seemed to be in a hurry but still I started to talk to him. Actually he just came from work and headed home as he was tired. And he wanted me to switch off the camera immediately. But I offered him 500 CZK for a short interview and suddenly the camera didn´t matter anymore and he had as much time as I needed. He lived in Prague, studied to become a mechanic and worked part-time as a life-guard to make some extra money... did he mention "extra money"?
title: Czech Hunter 222
